# random number generation test

+ pulse clock
= 250 clock@rate

+ random rnd
> clock@out rnd@clock

+ map scale
= 0 scale@imin
= 1 scale@imax
= 1 scale@omin
= 4 scale@omax
> rnd@out scale@in

+ round idx
> scale@out idx@in

+ select sel
> idx@out sel@index
= 48 sel@in1
= 50 sel@in2
= 51 sel@in3
= 53 sel@in4

+ miditofreq mtof
> sel@out mtof@in

+ sinosc osc
> mtof@out osc@freq

+ mult amp
> osc@out amp@in1
= 0.8 amp@in2

> amp@out out@l
> amp@out out@r

